						               													<description>In Rhodes: The Colossus, the first expansion to Rhodes, players may help to build the great statue The Colossus. Whether it will be finished in time is uncertain, though.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This expansion brings more strategy and excitement to the game. Introducing 16 new development tiles, a new temple with high potential for players who enjoy developing their estate, a second production option, and of course, the construction site of the Colossus. The game play is extended to 90-120 minutes!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In order to build the Colossus, bronze is a vital element. It is quite a scarce element in the game, therefore creating more tension and smart playing with new interaction in the temple, the production, and the Colossus site. The bonus track of the Colossus creates extra incentives for helping to build the Colossus and it creates interesting competition.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;As in Rhodes, The Colossus also creates interesting interaction and &amp;quot;cooperative&amp;quot; play, but still only one player can win this game. Now several tactics and strategies will give more options to the players to seize their victory in The Colossus.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
